<h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-100 mb-6">Quick Start</h1>

<p class="text-zinc-400 mb-6">
  Start a hub and connect your browser in under a minute.
</p>

<h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-200 mt-8 mb-3">1. Start your hub</h2>
<pre class="bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 rounded-lg p-4 text-sm text-zinc-300 font-mono overflow-x-auto mb-6"><code>cd your-project
botster start</code></pre>
<p class="text-zinc-400 mb-6">
  This launches the TUI and registers your hub with trybotster.com.
</p>

<h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-200 mt-8 mb-3">2. Connect your browser</h2>
<p class="text-zinc-400 mb-6">
  Visit <span class="font-mono text-zinc-300">trybotster.com</span> and scan the QR code displayed in the TUI, or use the connection URL.
</p>

<h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-200 mt-8 mb-3">3. Create an agent</h2>
<p class="text-zinc-400 mb-6">
  Once connected, create a new agent from the browser UI. Botster will create an isolated worktree and spawn Claude in a PTY.
</p>
